                "html": "<table><tr><td>spheroid</td><td>Bessel 1841</td></tr><tr><td>latitude origin</td><td>0.0</td></tr><tr><td>longitude origin</td><td>9 degrees E (zone 3)</td></tr><tr><td>false easting (m)</td><td>3500000</td></tr><tr><td>false northing</td><td>0.0</td></tr><tr><td>scale factor</td><td>1.</td></tr></table>",
